name: Synthesizer
description:
Limited edition of 7 prints
direct from the artist
ideal for 600x500 frame 3 colour limited edition screen prints. Printed on 600 x 500mm grey BFK Rives 100% cotton rag paper. Hand-pulled and signed by the artist. Shipped wrapped in acid-free tissue paper inside a cardboard poster tube.
As a result of being screenprinted by hand, some prints may vary slightly in colour or registration. This, however, is one of the charms of the process.
